              East Valley Women for Women accepts over 800 insurance plans, including most major carriers. We're committed to making quality healthcare accessible and affordable.
            </p>
            <a href="/insurance" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-semibold">
              View Accepted Insurance Plans ‚Üí
            </a>
